{"word":"παιδίσκη","slug":"παιδίσκη","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παιδίσκη</b></el> <el>(παιδίσκη, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Diminutive'>Dim.</a> of <a href='S:παῖς'><el>παῖς</el></a>\n<br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>h\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a young girl, maiden</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a young slave, courtesan</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}